    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 54 of a 12-week money program. The script targets the fear-of-depletion response that can follow a generous impulse: the quick calculation, the holding back, the guilt afterward. The reframe builds generosity as something that belongs in a wealthy life, not something you earn the right to once the account reaches a particular number.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
